;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">\n<cite class=\"citation web\">Lasich, Christina, M.D. (March 7, 2011). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.healthcentral.com/chronic-pain/c/23153/133392/inversion/\">\"The Upsides and Downsides of Inversion Therapy\"</a>. <a href=\"/wiki/HealthCentral\" title=\"HealthCentral\">HealthCentral</a><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">July 11,</span> 2015</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=The+Upsides+and+Downsides+of+Inversion+Therapy&amp;rft.pub=HealthCentral&amp;rft.date=2011-03-07&amp;rft.aulast=Lasich&amp;rft.aufirst=Christina%2C+M.D.&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.healthcentral.com%2Fchronic-pain%2Fc%2F23153%2F133392%2Finversion%2F&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AInversion+therapy\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nParsed by mw2146\nCached time: 20180919213831\nCache expiry: 1900800\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.092 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.121 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 203/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 0/1500000\nPost\u2010expand include size: 4953/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 81/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 1/500\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post\u2010expand size: 3704/5000000 bytes\nNumber of Wikibase entities loaded: 0/400\nLua time usage: 0.039/10.000 seconds\nLua memory usage: 1.91 MB/50 MB\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   97.776      1 -total\n 64.78%   63.338      1 Template:Reflist\n 42.91%   41.958      2 Template:Cite_web\n 30.81%   30.127      1 Template:Redire